OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780481194
OL,3,CAt least 11 people killed overnight in
OL,4,C'massive' Russian attacks on Ukraine
OL,6,FAt least 11 people have been killed in
OL,7,Fan overnight Russian assault on
OL,8,FUkraine.
OL,10,FFour people were killed in the
OL,11,Fcountry's capital, Kyiv and six were
OL,12,Fkilled in an attack on the central
OL,13,Fcity of Dnipro, where a subsequent
OL,14,Fattack killed a rescue worker
OL,15,Fattending to the scene.
OL,17,FMore than 100 people, including
OL,18,Fchildren, were wounded, according to
OL,19,FUkrainian officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
