OL,3,CAt least 11 people killed overnight in
OL,4,C'massive' Russian attacks on Ukraine
OL,6,FCombined missile and drone strikes
OL,7,Ftargeted the capital, damaging several
OL,8,Fresidential and commercial buildings,
OL,9,Fsparking fires and burning cars,
OL,10,Fauthorities said.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FKyiv Mayor Vitali Klitschko described
OL,18,Fthe overnight assault as a "massive
OL,19,Fenemy attack".
