CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780481194
OL,3,CAt least 11 people killed overnight in
OL,4,C'massive' Russian attacks on Ukraine
OL,6,FPreliminary reports indicated that
OL,7,Fthere were people trapped under the
OL,8,Frubble, Tymur Tkachenko, head of Kyiv
OL,9,Fcity military administration, wrote on
OL,10,FTelegram.
OL,12,FIn Dnipro a two-storey residential
OL,13,Fbuilding and part of a four-storey
OL,14,Fblock of flats were damaged, and
OL,15,Fpeople were left trapped beneath the
OL,16,Frubble of the larger building. More
OL,17,Fpeople were trapped under buildings in
OL,18,Fthe Podilskyi district in Kyiv after a
OL,19,Fnine-storey building was damaged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
